<subSubSection pageId="21" pageNumber="526" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1437,447,832]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,519,544]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Zerny" box="[327,494,520,544]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" refString="Zerny, H. (1912 a) Syntomidae. In: Wagner, H. (Ed.), Lepidopterorum Catalogus, Pars 7. W. Junk, Berlin, pp. 179." type="journal article" year="1912" yearSuffix="a">
Zerny (
<number box="[415,473,520,544]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" value="1912.0">1912</number>
a)
</bibRefCitation>
created this name as the objective replacement name for 
<taxonomicName authority="Rothschild, 1911" authorityName="Rothschild" authorityYear="1911" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Cosmosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mathani">
<emphasis box="[1194,1436,519,544]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">Cosmosoma mathani</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Rothschild" box="[151,343,556,581]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" refString="Rothschild, W. (1911) New Syntomidae in the Tring Museum. Novitates Zoologicae, 18, 24 - 45." type="journal article" year="1911">
Rothschild, 
<number box="[285,343,556,580]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" value="1911.0">1911</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, a junior primary homonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="Rothschild, 1910" authorityName="Rothschild" authorityYear="1910" box="[690,1126,556,581]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Cosmosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mathani">
<emphasis box="[690,925,556,581]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">Cosmosoma mathani</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Rothschild" box="[932,1126,556,581]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" refString="Rothschild, W. (1910) Descriptions of a new Hawk-moth and some new Syntomidae. Annals and Magazine of Natural History, 8 (5), 506 - 511. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222931008692806" type="journal article" year="1910">
Rothschild, 
<number box="[1066,1126,556,580]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" value="1910.0">1910</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. This action was ignored by 
<bibRefCitation author="Hampson" box="[151,337,592,616]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" refString="Hampson, G. F. (1914) Catalogue of the Lepidoptera Phalaenae in the British Museum, Supplement. vol. I. Catalogue of the Amatidae and Arctiadae (Nolinae and Lithosianae) in the collection of the British Museum. Printed by the order of the Trustees of the British Museum, London, 858 pp." type="book" year="1914">Hampson (1914</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Hampson" box="[351,410,591,616]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" refString="Hampson, G. F. (1915) Catalogue of the Lepidoptera Phalaenae in the British Museum, Supplement. Vol. I. Plates I-XLI. Printed by the order of the Trustees of the British Museum, London, 71 pls." type="book chapter" year="1915">1915</bibRefCitation>
), who also erroneously mentioned a male 
<typeStatus box="[907,955,592,616]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">type</typeStatus>
for 
<taxonomicName authority="Rothschild, 1911" authorityName="Rothschild" authorityYear="1911" box="[1009,1344,591,616]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Cosmosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mathani">
<emphasis box="[1009,1137,591,616]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">C. mathani</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Rothschild" box="[1147,1344,591,616]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" refString="Rothschild, W. (1911) New Syntomidae in the Tring Museum. Novitates Zoologicae, 18, 24 - 45." type="journal article" year="1911">
Rothschild, 
<number box="[1286,1344,592,616]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" value="1911.0">1911</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. Draudt (
<number box="[159,217,628,653]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" value="1915.0">1915</number>
) recognized the homonymy and adopted the name 
<taxonomicName box="[790,930,628,653]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Chrostosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="exomelan">
<emphasis box="[790,930,628,653]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">C. exomelan</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for 
<taxonomicName authority="Rothschild, 1911" authorityName="Rothschild" authorityYear="1911" box="[976,1301,628,653]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Cosmosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mathani">
<emphasis box="[976,1101,628,653]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">C. mathani</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Rothschild" box="[1108,1301,628,653]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" refString="Rothschild, W. (1911) New Syntomidae in the Tring Museum. Novitates Zoologicae, 18, 24 - 45." type="journal article" year="1911">
Rothschild, 
<number box="[1243,1301,628,652]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" value="1911.0">1911</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1437,447,832]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">
The new combination in 
<taxonomicName authority="Hubner" authorityName="Hubner" box="[509,759,663,688]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Chrostosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[509,658,663,688]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">Chrostosoma</emphasis>
Hübner
</taxonomicName>
, [
<number box="[784,845,664,688]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" value="1819.0">1819</number>
] of this species and others previously placed in 
<taxonomicName authority="Hubner" authorityName="Hubner" box="[151,382,700,725]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Cosmosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,288,701,724]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">Cosmosoma</emphasis>
Hübner
</taxonomicName>
, [
<number box="[401,462,700,724]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" value="1823.0">1823</number>
] is discussed in 
<bibRefCitation author="Pinheiro" box="[649,944,700,725]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" refString="Pinheiro, L. R. &amp; Duarte, M. (2013) Taxonomic notes on Ctenuchina, Euchromiina, and Phaegopterina (Lepidoptera, Erebidae, Arctiinae, Arctiini). Florida Entomologist, 96 (2), 351 - 359. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1653 / 024.096.0255" type="journal article" year="2013">
Pinheiro &amp; Duarte (
<number box="[875,936,700,724]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" value="2013.0">2013</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. 
<taxonomicName box="[956,1221,700,725]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Chrostosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="exomelan">
<emphasis box="[956,1221,700,725]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">Chrostosoma exomelan</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is here maintained in this genus merely because it is not possible at this moment to ascertain its taxonomic placement, which is almost certainly not in 
<taxonomicName box="[338,486,772,797]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Chrostosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[338,486,772,797]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">Chrostosoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. This species closely resembles one of the female phenotypes of 
<taxonomicName authority="Walker, 1856" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1856" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Phoenicoprocta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vacillans">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="526">Phoenicoprocta vacillans</emphasis>
(Walker, 
<number box="[361,421,807,832]" pageId="21" pageNumber="526" value="1856.0">1856</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
